Odunayo Folasade Adekuoroye (amụrụ ka ọnwa  Disemba dị na ụbọchị1993) bụ onye Naijiria na-agba mgba. O sonyere na asọmpi freestyle ụmụ nwanyị 53 kg na 2014 Commonwealth Games ebe ọ meriri nrite ọla edo na 2015 World Wrestling Championships ebe ọ merie ọla nchara. O meriri nrite ọlaọcha na freestyle ụmụ nwanyị 55 kilogram 2017 World Wrestling Championships.
